#: .\bionics.json
msgid "Fire Extinguisher"
msgstr "灭火器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Fire Extinguisher'}
#: .\bionics.json
msgid ""
"A small, retractable launcher resides in the palm of your hand through your "
"arm. The system will automatically produce small gelatinous orbs that when "
"launched into fire will rapidly expand into a fire fighting foam. "
msgstr "一个可伸缩的小型发射器通过你的手臂置于掌心。该系统会自动产生小型凝胶球体，发射到火中时会迅速膨胀成灭火泡沫。"

