#: .\furniture\furniture_override.json
msgid "Autodoc Mk. XI"
msgstr "自动医疗机 Mk. XI"

#. ~ Description for Autodoc Mk. XI
#: .\furniture\furniture_override.json
msgid ""
"A surgical apparatus used for installation and uninstallation of bionics.  "
"It's only as skilled as its operator."
msgstr "一种用于安装和卸载仿生装置的手术设备。其技术水平仅取决于操作者。"

#: .\furniture\furniture_override.json
msgid "whack!"
msgstr "啪！"

#: .\furniture\furniture_override.json
msgid "Autodoc operation couch"
msgstr "自动手术台"

#. ~ Description for Autodoc operation couch
#: .\furniture\furniture_override.json
msgid ""
"A plush red sofa made less comfortable by the medical machinery directly "
"above it.  It has a single leather strap on the right armrest."
msgstr "一张豪华的红色沙发，因正上方的医疗设备而舒适度降低。右侧扶手上有一条皮质绑带。"

#: .\furniture\furniture_override.json
msgid "smash!"
msgstr "砸！"

