#: .\items\books.json
msgid "BioCo Chemical Reference"
msgid_plural "BioCo Chemical References"
msgstr[0] "BioCo 化学参考手册"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'BioCo Chemical Reference', 'str_pl': 'BioCo
#. Chemical References'}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"A dense and oddly non-technical binder full of detailed descriptions of "
"various chemical processes used by the BioCo Chemical Engine. While a lot of"
" these are beyond you, there's a few you think you might be able to "
"replicate."
msgstr ""
"一本厚重且出奇地非技术性的活页夹，详细描述了 BioCo 化学引擎使用的各种化学过程。虽然其中大部分内容超出了你的理解范围，但你觉得有一些或许能够复现。"

